%^GREEN%^BOLD%^Rangers are able to select favored enemies and favored terrain as part of their class features.
%^CYAN%^BOLD%^Inquisitors also choose an enemy type for their Bane feature.

Below is a list of the favored enemy types on the left, and the creatures included in those types on the right.

    %^RED%^aberrations --------: beholder, illithid, mind flayer, aberration
    %^ORANGE%^animals ------------: snake, serpent, warthog, jaguar, wolf, rat, tiger, reptile, dinosaur, dino, spider, deer, snake, horse, mare, stallion, animal
    %^YELLOW%^constructs ---------: construct, golem, sandman, sandling
    %^BLUE%^dwarves ------------: dwarf, dwarves, duergar, construct
    %^GREEN%^dragonkin ----------: dragonkin, kobold, draconian, dragon, elven-dragon, dragonet, pseudodragon, drake, wyvern
    %^MAGENTA%^elementals ---------: elemental, genasi, earth genasi, air genasi, water genasi, fire genasi, efreet, djinn, marid, genie
    %^RED%^elves --------------: elf, elves, half-elf, drow, half-drow, szarkai
    %^ORANGE%^fey ----------------: nymph, satyr, dryad, pixie, brownie, feytouched, fey
    %^YELLOW%^giants -------------: voadkyn, firbolg, giant, titan, troll
    %^BLUE%^goblins ------------: goblin, bugbear, hobgoblin, goblinoid
    %^GREEN%^humans -------------: human, shade, half-elf, half-orc, half-ogre, half-drow, genasi, feytouched, aasimar, tiefling
    %^MAGENTA%^lizardfolk ---------: lizardfolk, yuan-ti, saurian, salamander, lizardman, firenewt
    %^RED%^magical beasts -----: owlbear, grimlock, jackalwere, wolfwere, ooze, worm, pegataur, griffon, hydra, shadow, magical beast
    %^ORANGE%^monstrous humanoids : monstrous humanoids, beastkin, wemic, centaur, ratkin, minotaur, gnoll, kitsune, werewolf, wererat, weretiger, alaghi, monstrous humanoid
    %^YELLOW%^ogres --------------: ogre, ogre-mage, half-ogre, ogroid
    %^BLUE%^orcs ---------------: orc, half-orc, orog, tanarukk, orcoid
    %^GREEN%^outsiders ----------: deva, solar, aasimar, angel, demon, devil, imp, tiefling, githyanki, githzerai, outsider
    %^MAGENTA%^plants -------------: plants, shambler, shambling mound, tree, vine, plant
    %^RED%^smallfolk ----------: gnome, halfling, kender, derro, pech, smallfolk
    %^ORANGE%^undead -------------: ghost, skeleton, lich, zombie, ghast, entity, spirit, undead, wraith, wight

See also : Favored Enemy, Favored Terrain, Ranger, Bane, Inquisitor